🎯 Revision Hook
When revising:

“Minimum jumps” → Greedy range expansion.

Track farthest and currentEnd.

Increment jumps when you finish a range.

If stuck → return -1.

👉 Memory trick:
“Expand range, count jumps, stop if stuck.”
